      "content": "Let's add some grit to the scene. A typical dinner conversation in a Black household can veer into micromanaging debates, like whose turn it is to do the dishes or who spent too much money on groceries. Or, elders might disapprove of their adult children's career choices or life choices, leading to good-natured but sharp-tongued teasing. Young adults might challenge the traditional wisdom of their elders, sparking a lively discussion that could escalate into good-natured jokes or, in some cases, fiery arguments. Amidst the chaos, someone might let out a humorous aside, quickly diffusing tension.",
